{subhead}Amiga Forums{def}
{left}
{pp}
 Amiga Forums has been launched upon the Amiga Community.
{pp}
 The Forums are a joint effort between  AmiBench,  Amiga  Resource  and
 Striatum.org.  Their  main  role is to provide support and information
 for worldwide Amiga users.
{pp}
 Currently the following forums are available:-
